  <brief_title>The Role of Tomotherapy in Hypofractionated/Dose Escalated Conformal Radiation Treatment for High Risk Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Tomotherapy (Dynamic IMRT and Megavoltage CT Scanning) in Hypofractionated/Dose Escalated Conformal Radiation Treatment Using Magnetic Resonance Spectroscopy (MRS) Scans to Predict and Document the Pattern of Local Failure for High Risk Prostate Cancer</official_title>
