    <measure>Rectal Toxicity</measure>
    <time_frame>5 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>Determine the acute and late rectal toxicity of high-dose short-course hypofractionated radiotherapy in five weeks in the treatment of high rish prostate cancer.</description>
